{"tid":845694,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"探討人生投資策略","createTime":"2018-10-03T00:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T05:22:33.000Z","uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"68dcafdcb0b69f9ab54723036a5641569cff2da9","tid":845694,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T00:56:31.000Z","msg":"身為一個窮三代，<br />\n天時地利人和都喺相對劣勢。<br />\n<br />\n如果再按照正常港豬生存之道，<br />\n到最後只會變成大輸家。<br />\n<br />\n唔好講咩刷手抽，<br />\n因為有冇輪迴都冇人知。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣嘅可以一齊討論吓人生應該點投資，<br />\n希望將來大家都可以贖身唔洗再做豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6aa3e139c8ba72d7448838d77aad9aa0eacc64","tid":845694,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T00:58:46.000Z","msg":"我就知道又係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab9007bea01ea1569221607f82ba163dc9f7a35","tid":845694,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b6aa3e139c8ba72d7448838d77aad9aa0eacc64","tid":845694,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T00:58:46.000Z","msg":"我就知道又係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T00:59:12.000Z","msg":"係我又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849df8fa5160d7e2438d0e845ffd46d4544395d2","tid":845694,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ab9007bea01ea1569221607f82ba163dc9f7a35","tid":845694,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b6aa3e139c8ba72d7448838d77aad9aa0eacc64","tid":845694,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T00:58:46.000Z","msg":"我就知道又係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T00:59:12.000Z","msg":"係我又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T00:59:59.000Z","msg":"冇乜點"},{"pid":"98761065